<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Features</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">


<ListItem>
<Paragraph>Essential Chart supports the customizable <Bold>ToolBar </Bold>. It helps to customize the chart properties in run time.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>



</List>
<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The check box <Bold>"Show Close Button"</Bold> enables or disables the close button in chart toolbar.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The check box <Bold>"Show TitleBar"</Bold> enables or disables the title bar of a chart toolbar.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Background"</Bold> selects the background color of the chart toolbar.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Header Background"</Bold> selects the background color of the header in chart toolbar.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The Text block <Bold>"Old Value"</Bold> Represents the last selected ToolBar item.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The Text block <Bold>"New Value"</Bold> Represents the newly selected ToolBar item.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The Button <Bold>"Add ToolBar Item"</Bold> To add new ToolBarItem.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The check box <Bold>"Show Toolbar"</Bold>enables or disables the chart toolbar.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The Button <Bold>"Close ToolBar"</Bold> To close the ToolBar</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
</List>



